name: Induskush Shabazz
description:
Induskush Shabazz is the last release from the 10 track Nubio Manifesto project. 

All other tracks can be found as single releases on all major streaming platforms 

Induskush Shabazz captures the sounds of two nations, Africa and India in an Afrohouse framework

If you enjoy getting down to syncopation check out the vibrations of these two nations in an Afrohouse framework 

The artwork depicts how many go through the world as the seen and unseen
